title: The Weekend Bite by Wall Street Breakfast - Week Ending February 11th, 2022
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: This week we are joined by Andy Constan, Founder of Damped Springs Advisors, and Nicholas Colas, Co-Founder of DataTrek to discuss the hot CPI numbers, The Federal Reserve, rate hikes, supply chains, year-end price targets, and so much more!
